  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What's happening-- the first thing was the Russian front.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- that was the beginning of the real world.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- that was-- it's in the wrong sequence.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the safe houses were only in the last year of the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The safe houses were not-- there were no safe houses until towards the-- towards the second half of 1944.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Germans have occupied Hungary on the 19th of March, 1944.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from then on, not in-- not in the cities-- so not in Budapest-- but all the surrounding suburbs, they set up ghettos.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we entered the ghetto [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] first week of April, if I remember, something like this-- two, three weeks after the Germans occupied Hungary.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And occupied Hungary-- when I say occupied it, they only occupied Hungary because-- I don't know how much history has-- has recorded it, but I'm sure it has-- that-- that the government of Hungary, Horthy, Miklos, has shown reluctance to deport the Jews, and was-- was not going to carry through the orders of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was-- he was-- but he was, unfortunately, almost the only one who-- who would have stood up to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, from then on, he was-- most of the time, he was on house arrest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was only a figurehead after that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So this is why-- this is the reason why the Germans occupied Hungary, to make sure that their people are in power-- their-- their people-- the Hungarian people are in power, and not the government, which they would have had difficulty with of achieving whatever they want to achieve.",
      "word_count": 49
    }
  ],
